$PAR
\(\hskip 23pt x\)
$BR
\( 17\vert\overline{7892} \)
$BR
\(\hskip 15 pt yy\)
$PAR
 In the starting situation x = \{ans_rule(1)\} and yy=\{ans_rule(3)\} 
END_TEXT
